'''Bradfield Combust with Stanningfield''' is a [[civil parish]] in the [[St Edmundsbury (borough)|St Edmundsbury]] borough of [[Suffolk]], [[England]].  

According to the 2001 census it had a population of 503.  The parish covers [[Bradfield Combust]] and [[Stanningfield]], about 6 miles south of [[Bury St Edmunds]].

